WEBVTT

00:00.673 --> 00:02.274
<i>Previously on "Heartland":</i>

00:02.341 --> 00:04.676
<i>I just can't help but wonder</i>

00:04.744 --> 00:07.012
what I did to deserve
such an extravagant gift.

00:07.080 --> 00:09.581
Amy, what the hell
do you think you're doing?

00:09.649 --> 00:12.184
I told you, my dad wants me
to work with this horse,

00:12.252 --> 00:13.485
and so far,

00:13.552 --> 00:14.586
you've ignored everything
I've said.

00:14.654 --> 00:15.820
When Shane left
the last time

00:15.888 --> 00:17.789
he was convinced
that my dad and his mom

00:17.856 --> 00:19.056
have a thing
for each other,

00:19.124 --> 00:20.258
and then all of a sudden

00:20.325 --> 00:21.793
Shane and Miranda
just disappear?

00:21.860 --> 00:23.694
You still haven't
told your girls?

00:23.762 --> 00:26.130
I haven't told anyone,
except for you and Jack.

00:27.666 --> 00:29.200
Let me outta the truck,
Jack!

00:29.268 --> 00:32.101
Just think of it as
a friendly intervention,

00:32.170 --> 00:34.470
and an opportunity for you
to settle this Shane thing

00:34.538 --> 00:36.206
once and for all.

00:36.274 --> 00:37.607
If you let Tim
into your life,

00:37.675 --> 00:39.409
Shane won't just be
gaining a father,

00:39.476 --> 00:41.211
he'll be gaining
a whole family.

00:41.279 --> 00:44.347
I can't compete
with you guys.

